    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world devoid of originality, where talentless hacks copy your every move, you gotta use their stupidity against them to come out on top. Lucky Me is a puzzle shooter game inspired by rap music video and rap tropes that sets you up against your own copycats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your deductive logic is the only thing standing between you and being blasted away. Line up your shots, pull the trigger and survive the bullet storm. Out of ammo? Use their stupidity against them and come out on top. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712270/extras/5965762baa340431a0be5de7f47059b2.poster.avif?t=1748566326\" width=600 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712270/extras/5965762baa340431a0be5de7f47059b2.webm?t=1748566326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1712270/extras/5965762baa340431a0be5de7f47059b2.mp4?t=1748566326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LUCKY ME FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >INNOVATION - experience a true hybrid game, bringing together puzzles, shooting and rap tropes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >MULTIPLE GAME MODES - adapt your strategy with every new gameplay mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >INFINITE MODE - test your shooting skills defeating wave after wave of enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >LEVEL EDITOR - remix your own levels and challenge your friends.</p></li></ul>",
